Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.17,0:21:25.58,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}Bleed my heart dry
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.58,0:21:29.60,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}Leave me here to die
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.60,0:21:31.69,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}It’ll be all on you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.69,0:21:32.94,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}Said, “gimme your heart”
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.94,0:21:35.73,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}So I filled it up with all of my love
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.73,0:21:39.13,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}Gave it to you, trusted that you would keep it safe
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.54,0:21:42.66,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}It thrived upon your vibe
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.66,0:21:44.83,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}Beating in sync with yours at night
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.83,0:21:48.68,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}You poured your soul into mine with just a wink
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.07,0:21:52.49,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}So why don’t you want my heart no more?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.49,0:21:54.88,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}It’s gathering dust on your bedroom floor
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.88,0:21:57.95,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}Do what you want, decision’s yours
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.95,0:21:59.88,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}I’ll be alright
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.62,0:22:02.65,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}If you won’t take it
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.65,0:22:06.60,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}You might as well bleed it
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.60,0:22:07.83,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}Squeeze it like a lemon
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.83,0:22:09.81,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}Like a rag you’ll throw away
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.44,0:22:12.65,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}Bleed my heart dry
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.65,0:22:15.92,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}Leave me here to die
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.75,0:22:19.78,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}It’ll be all on you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.78,0:22:21.77,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}I know you’ll do what’s right
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.77,0:22:25.70,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}And be right by my side
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.15,0:22:28.48,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}Won’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.48,0:22:30.89,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}Why won’t, why won’t you bleed my heart dry?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.89,0:22:34.54,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}Why don’t you leave me here to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.54,0:22:37.79,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}Why won’t you bleed my heart dry?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.79,0:22:40.02,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}You know that I’ll put it all on you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.02,0:22:43.96,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}I trust you’ll know just what to do
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.55,0:22:49.17,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}I’ll be right here, forever waiting for you
Dialogue: 1,0:21:23.17,0:21:25.58,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}榨干我的心脏
Dialogue: 1,0:21:25.58,0:21:29.60,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}留我一人等死
Dialogue: 1,0:21:29.60,0:21:31.69,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}全都是因为你
Dialogue: 1,0:21:31.69,0:21:32.94,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}你说“给我你的心”
Dialogue: 1,0:21:32.94,0:21:35.73,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}于是我用全部的爱将其填满
Dialogue: 1,0:21:35.73,0:21:39.13,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}把它给你  相信你会保管好
Dialogue: 1,0:21:40.54,0:21:42.66,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}它在你的熏陶下蓬勃
Dialogue: 1,0:21:42.66,0:21:44.83,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}在夜晚与你心跳同步
Dialogue: 1,0:21:44.83,0:21:48.68,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}你只用眨眼就让我魂牵梦绕
Dialogue: 1,0:21:50.07,0:21:52.49,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}为什么你不再想要我的心了？
Dialogue: 1,0:21:52.49,0:21:54.88,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}它在你的卧室地板积灰
Dialogue: 1,0:21:54.88,0:21:57.95,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}做你想做的  都取决于你
Dialogue: 1,0:21:57.95,0:21:59.88,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}我没事的
Dialogue: 1,0:22:00.62,0:22:02.65,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}如果你不接受它
Dialogue: 1,0:22:02.65,0:22:06.60,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}或许也会榨干它
Dialogue: 1,0:22:06.60,0:22:07.83,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}像挤压一个柠檬
Dialogue: 1,0:22:07.83,0:22:09.81,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}像一块无用抹布
Dialogue: 1,0:22:10.44,0:22:12.65,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}榨干我的心脏
Dialogue: 1,0:22:12.65,0:22:15.92,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}留我一人等死
Dialogue: 1,0:22:16.75,0:22:19.78,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}全都是因为你
Dialogue: 1,0:22:19.78,0:22:21.77,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}我知道你会做正确的事
Dialogue: 1,0:22:21.77,0:22:25.70,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}陪在我的身边
Dialogue: 1,0:22:26.15,0:22:28.48,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}对吗？
Dialogue: 1,0:22:28.48,0:22:30.89,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}为什么你不榨干我的心脏？
Dialogue: 1,0:22:30.89,0:22:34.54,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}为什么你不留我一人等死？
Dialogue: 1,0:22:34.54,0:22:37.79,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}为什么你不榨干我的心脏？
Dialogue: 1,0:22:37.79,0:22:40.02,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}你知道我会全部交给你
Dialogue: 1,0:22:40.02,0:22:43.96,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}我相信你知道该做什么
Dialogue: 1,0:22:44.55,0:22:49.17,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}我会在这里  永远等着你
